#

Honey Soy Glazed Salmon

25 min
$12.5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

FishSoy

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh Protein

Cuisine:

AmericanAsian

Course:

Main DishDinner

Tags:

QuickHealthyDinnerEasy

Description

A deliciously sweet and savory salmon dish, perfect for a quick weeknight dinner!

Ingredients

  • salmon fillets: 2 (6 oz each)
  • honey: 1/4 cup
  • soy sauce: 1/4 cup
  • garlic (minced): 2 cloves
  • ginger (grated): 1 tsp
  • green onions (sliced): 2
  • sesame seeds (optional): 1 tbsp
